5px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(239, 239, 238); line-height: 14px; font-size: 12px; position: relative; vertical-align: top;\">&nbsp;<i style=\"position: absolute; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 10px; height: 7px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -100px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"></i></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"display: inline-block; margin-right: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><i style=\"float: left; margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 5px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -100px -145px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"></i><span style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">个园(1-3小时)</span></span></li></ul></div><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 180px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 940px;\"><ul style=\"margin: 0px -15px 0px 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; position: absolute; height: 100px; width: 1425px; left: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin-right: 15px; list-style: none; float: left; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: inline-block; position: relative; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a data-t=\"poi\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5430250.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img data-original=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s7/M00/29/D2/wKgB6lPDZG6AKw_OAAbyqRbs7AI92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s7/M00/29/D2/wKgB6lPDZG6AKw_OAAbyqRbs7AI92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"display: inline;\" class=\"mCS_img_loaded\"><div style=\"padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 15px;