; display: inline; width: 260px; border: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\">4月到9月是伦敦最美的时候，鲜花盛开，阳光温和。冬季则是最佳购物季。想在行前更深入了解伦敦，推荐观看BBC的纪录片《伦敦一览》。</p></li></ul></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">总结</h3><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><ul style=\"margin: 25px auto 30px; padding-top: 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; width: auto; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><li style=\"margin-left: 22px; padding-left: 22px; list-style: none; float: left; display: inline; width: 260px; border-left: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\">线路设计包含14个伦敦经典景点，从舌尖品味伦敦（英式早餐、下午茶），深度探索艺术文化（博物馆、西区观剧）和特色集市，做个最有范儿的伦敦客。</p></li></ul></h2>', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `product_desc` VALUES ('155206252002308', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">景点概况</h2><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><span id=\"mdd_poi_desc\" style=\"display: inline;\">巴黎是文艺爱好者的天堂，众多顶级博物馆带你领略欧洲艺术的灿烂荣光，名人故居让你追寻大师成长的轨迹，你可以在这里遇见蒙娜丽莎、断臂的维纳斯、雨果、巴尔扎克等等。巴黎也是法兰西民族悠久历史和灿烂文化的集中展现地，一座座美轮美奂的建筑静静地看着这个城市的变化，也在诉说这个城市的故事。作为享誉世界的浪漫之都，巴黎也是蜜月圣地，你大可不必去热门景点排长队，牵着恋人的手在塞纳河畔悠游漫步，走过一座座桥，或者在法式花园的草坪上晒太阳都是体验这里浪漫风情的绝佳方式。</span></div>', '<dl style=\"list-style: none; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 12px;\"><dt style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 5px; list-style: none; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">路线概览</dt><dd style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; visibility: visible;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D1</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11967.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">卢浮宫(3小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12385.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">杜乐丽花园(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11968.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">协和广场(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11944.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">亚历山大三世桥(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6563261.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">塞纳河游船(2小时)</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D2</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5745926.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">奥赛博物馆(1.5小时)</a><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12400.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; cursor: pointer;\"><font color=\"#000000\">橘园美术馆(机动选择)</font></a>&nbsp;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11945.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">香榭丽舍大街(30分钟)</a><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/93312.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">Laduree(1小时)</a><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11930.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴黎凯旋门(30分钟)</a><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span><font color=\"#666666\">&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11962.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">埃菲尔铁塔(1小时)</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D3</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12413.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">卢森堡公园(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/93259.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">花神咖啡馆(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11965.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">先贤祠(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12230.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">莎士比亚书店(30分钟)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11942.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴黎圣母院(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12234.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">蓬皮杜国家艺术文化中心(1小时)</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D4</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/93215.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">爱墙(30分钟)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11947.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">法国圣心大教堂(1小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5504662.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴黎歌剧院(30分钟)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11956.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴黎老佛爷奥斯曼旗舰店(3小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11955.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">法国春天百货(3小时)</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D5</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12228.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">凡尔赛宫(5小时)</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D6</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6653494.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">莫奈花园(2小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/93279.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">枫丹白露宫(4小时)</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/12678.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴尔比宗(2小时)</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"float: left; margin-left: -40px;\">D7</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/9082034.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">巴黎迪士尼乐园(6-8小时)</a></p></div></dd></dl><ul style=\"margin: 25px auto 30px; padding-top: 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; width: auto; border-top: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><li style=\"list-style: none; float: left; display: inline; width: 260px; border: 0px;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Tips</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\">郊区的景点强烈推荐参加一日游系列，若4人以上也可以选择包车（含司机），不建议租车自驾，路线不熟的情况下停车较耽搁游玩时间</p></li><li style=\"margin-left: 22px; padding-left: 22px; list-style: none; float: left; display: inline; width: 260px; border-left: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">总结</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\">7日内不仅畅游市区内的世界顶级博物馆、地标及建筑，还能去到凡尔赛宫，枫丹白露、迪士尼等大巴黎郊区的景点，以及莫奈花园、巴比松之类的艺术村。</p></li></ul>', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `product_desc` VALUES ('155211029138720', '<p>挪威位于斯堪的纳维亚半岛之上，半岛上斯堪的纳维亚山脉纵贯挪威全境，因此在地形上，挪威主要是以高原和山地为主，而且面积约占整个国土的三分之二以上。斯堪的纳维亚山脉作为欧洲为数不多的大型山脉，最高峰加尔赫峰海拔2468米，由于纬度较高，以及暖流降雨的影响，形成了布满山脊的雪山冰川。</p>', '<dt style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; list-style: none; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-weight: 400;\">路线概览</dt><dd style=\"list-style: none; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; visibility: visible;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/36510.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">斯塔万格</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61854.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">吕瑟峡湾</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; line-height: 100px;\">→</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/116891.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); cursor: pointer;\">海于格松</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 10px; background: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;) -80px 0px no-re